Minimum requirements
----------------------
    * GTK 3.4
    * glib/gio 2.32
    * speex/speexdsp 1.0
    * libpeas 1.0
    * gmodule
    * libsoup 2.4


Fedora packages
-----------------

# Req: libcapi20

# Base
sudo yum install autoconf automake gtk3-devel intltool libtool speex-devel libsndfile-devel libxml2-devel libsoup-devel libpeas-devel spandsp-devel

# Plugins
libnotify-devel
evolution-devel
pulseaudio-libs-devel
libsecret-devel
